Program: Discovery
Title: The fourth dimension - more than meets the eye
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrxn3
Last Broadcast Date: 14 June 2000
Documentary which explores the theory of a hypothetical universe. Physics is pointing to the existence of a fourth dimension, and its implications open up science fiction-type possibilities. There could even be further dimensions, according to string theory, as the programme discovers.